                "roles": [
                    "bot"
                ],
                "image": "http://ddragon.leagueoflegends.com/cdn/7.12.1/img/item/3087.png "
            }
        ]

## Roles [/api/roles]

### Get Roles [GET]

Get information about all the roles in the game.

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "type": "bot",
                "champions":[
                    "draven",
                    "vayne",
                    ...
                ],
                "items": [
                    "infinityedge",
                    "phantomdancer",
                    ...
                ],
                "subtype": "marksman",
                "image": "/images/bot"
            },
            {
                "type": "top",
                "champions":[
                    "renekton",
                    "riven",
                    ...
                ],
                "items": [
                    "randiunsomen",
                    "titanichydra",
                    ...
                ],
                "subtype": [
                    "fighter",
                    "tank"
                ],
                "image": "/images/top"
            },
            ...
        ]

### Get A Role by Type [GET /api/roles/{type}]

Get information about a role by its type, which must contain only lowercase letters.

